{"tid":656494,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[數學題]14/2/2016- 14/4/2018超唔超過兩年？","createTime":"2018-05-07T09:58:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T09:58:36.000Z","uid":126175,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e3c6db50cd343dd5d59d99e1629f03d3d4fb0dea","tid":656494,"uid":126175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T09:58:36.000Z","msg":"究竟仲講緊兩年冇輸12碼既小學雞有冇獨立考證能力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/656130/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/656130/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">《馬卡報》指出，自從2016年的2月14日對陣切爾達的比賽中，巴塞被圭德蒂攻入一粒12碼，而在那之後的差不多2年的時間里，巴塞踢了74場西甲聯賽，但卻再也沒有被判罰過12碼。與此同時，巴塞則獲得32次12碼機會。在這兩年多的時間里，西甲總共出現了219粒12碼，但巴塞卻沒被判罰過一次。<br />\n<br />\n新浪網 2018-01-29 09:06:30</span><br />\n<br />\n邊個先係小學雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}